@5400 = ~Well now… what have we here? I had begun to think nothing roamed these streets but spiders and scorpions.~
@5401 = ~These ruins are now under the dominion of Vhaeraun’s chosen. By trespassing here, you have declared yourselves our enemies. And enemies are to be erased.~
@5402 = ~We will see about that!~
@5403 = ~I merely need to prepare an antidote. Once that is done, I will be on my way.~
@5404 = ~I did not clear this whole place of vermin just to let a pack of Drow settle in!~
@5405 = ~How charmingly uncivilized of you.~
@5406 = ~You truly believe we would allow you to walk away, now that you have seen us?~
@5407 = ~Oh! One among your rabble carries another amulet of that vanished Mythrien. Like me. Soon I will possess *two* such relics.~
@5408 = ~Enough talk. Slaughter them! Let us educate this <PRO_RACE> in the cost of defying the Masked Lord’s faithful!~
